TEXT.S: Tjacekes i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Tjacekes. u kasalumaluma' nu Tjacekes sa, 83 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 278 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 273 ku tademaw, pakalatu 98%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 5 ku tademaw, pakalatu 2%. u kasabinacadan, Paiwan 95%, zumazuma 3%.
